4Ô∏è‚É£ Detailed Architecture (Text Form)

Step-by-Step Pipeline

1. Document Ingestion

User uploads PDF or image.

PDF is converted to PNG/JPG.


2. Preprocessing

Resize + Normalize

Remove noise

Segment important regions (amounts, tables)


3. Image Forensics Engine

Includes 5 modules:

1. ELA (Error Level Analysis)
Highlights edited or recompressed areas.


2. Noise Analysis
Detects irregular noise in tampered areas.


3. JPEG Artifact Analysis
If only parts of document were re-saved, compression changes.


4. Metadata Extraction
Detect if PDF was edited in Photoshop/Canva.


5. Font Consistency Analysis
Amount/Name fields are checked for font-size differences.



4. OCR Engine

Extracts text using Tesseract or EasyOCR

Compares extracted text with typical bank patterns


5. ML Classification

A hybrid model:

CNN on ELA image

RandomForest/XGBoost on forensic features

Combined to predict ‚ÄúReal / Fake‚Äù


6. Report Generation

Fraud score

Highlighted tampered regions

PDF summary

Reasons for detection



