6Ô∏è‚É£ Data Sources (Clearly Stated)

We are NOT using real bank customer data.
Only safe, public, or synthetic data.

1. Synthetic Bank Statements

Build our own bank statement templates using Python or HTML

Generate 200‚Äì300 genuine statements

Create tampered versions by:

Changing amounts

Editing text

Copy-paste from other documents

Adding artificial compression



2. Public Sample Statements

Download masked/dummy statement PDFs from:

HDFC, ICICI, SBI sample formats

Global open sample PDFs


3. Open Data (Optional)

Use transaction datasets from Kaggle to generate realistic tables.

Dataset Size Goal

200 genuine

600 tampered variants

~800 total images



