9Ô∏è‚É£ Summary

‚ÄúWe are building an AI system that uses image forensics and machine learning to automatically detect manipulated or fake bank statements, using synthetic data, OCR, ELA, metadata analysis and a classification model. The solution will be provided as a working demo + open-source toolkit.